features.text:
#Bored Mummy Waking Up 

Thousands of years ago, the human race believed in the power of the spirits, they lives among us. These spirits were our guiding light - helping us to build kingdoms and fight bloody battles that ended in glorious victories. For many lifetimes, the wandering spirits were mankinds most faithful Guardians.

Under the watchful eyes of the Guardians, humans constructed the greatest wonders the Universe have seen, such as The Great Pyramid of Giza, Great Wall of China, or the Colosseum.

However, mankind soon became blinded by greed and lust for power. Toxic waste and deforestation gradually led to the ruin and devastation of our world. We were plagued by diseases and climate change, which brought upon catastrophic damages to the mighty kingdom that our Guardians have once helped us build.

Time is running out. We must save whats left of the world by summoning the strongest Guardian of prehistoric times from the Divine Chronosphere. Awaken the ancient legends to harness their power to restore earth and reinstate peace and order!

#Destiny awaits you....

features.text:
#Divine Chronosphere

Bored Mummy Waking Up is a limited edition NFT collection or unique digital collectibles thriving on the Ethereum blockchain. Owning BMWU tokens will grant you an exclusive membership and access to the Divine Chronosphere.

Within the Divine Chronosphere, you can summon your Guardian from the Book of Death. Call upon your Guardian to fight along your side in this mortal realm, or lead you to the other realm and start a new world.


All BMWU owner get to choose to join mortal realm, tech realm or spirit realm.  

All 8,888 BMWU will be ready for summon on the launch day on 8th Aug 12AM EST.
